test_run:cmd("setopt delimiter ';'")
---
- true
...
function do_long_thing()
    box.begin()
    box.space.test3:replace{100, 1, 'new'}
    while not finish_long_thing do
        fiber.sleep(0.01)
    end
    box.commit()
end;
